English: Do as many correct operations as you can in 1 minute
Spanish: Haz tantas operaciones correctas como puedas en 1 minuto

English: music: "The Path" by Syntactic / CC BY
Spanish: musica: "The Path" by Syntactic / CC BY

English: ROTATE THE CUBE TO THE CELL WITH THE CORRECT ANSWER TO ADVANCE
Spanish: ROTA EL CUBO HACIA LA CELDA CON EL RESULTADO CORRECTO PARA AVANZAR

English: THE COLOR OF THE BACKGROUND AND THE CUBE INDICATE THE CURRENT OPERATION
Spanish: EL COLOR DEL FONDO Y EL CUBO INDICAN LA OPERACION ACTUAL

English: WHEN THE CUBE TOUCHES A COLORED CELL, ITS OPERATION CHANGES
Spanish: CUANDO EL CUBO TOCA UNA CELDA DE COLOR, CAMBIA DE OPERACION

English: YOU CAN GO BACK OVER CLEARED CELLS
Spanish: PUEDES RETROCEDER POR LAS CELDAS YA DESPEJADAS

English: THERE ARE NO CELLS WITH DECIMAL NUMBERS, ALL RESULTS ARE INTEGERS
Spanish: NO HAY CELDAS CON NUMEROS DECIMALES, TODOS LOS RESULTADOS SON ENTEROS

English: FOR DIVISIONS, THE CORRECT ANSWER IS THE QUOTIENT. IF IT EXISTS, THE REMAINDER IS DISPLAYED SEPARATELY FROM THE RESULT.
Spanish: PARA LAS DIVISIONES, LA RESPUESTA CORRECTA ES EL COCIENTE. SI EXISTE RESTO, SE MUESTRA APARTE DEL RESULTADO.
